#+-------------------------------------------------------------------+
#  Fix alt tabbing black screen: https://www.protondb.com/app/40970
#+-------------------------------------------------------------------+
Type WINEPREFIX=/path to your steamapps/steamapps/compatdata/40970/pfx/ winecfg in terminal the like comrades advised in the comments below.
2nd step: Graphics tab > check "capture the mouse" and "emulate a virtual desktop". You may need that to freely switch windows by pressing alt+tab.
